data.description: This nice, ranch style home is move-in ready. There are 3 bedrooms on the main floor and 2 in the basement. One has an egress window, the other is non-conforming. There is a full bathroom on the main level and a 3/4 bathroom in the basement. The kitchen has lots of counter space and storage. The laundry is in the basement, along with an office, pantry, family room and storeroom. There is vinyl plank flooring upstairs and downstairs, with carpet in the bedrooms and ceramic tile in the main bathroom and laundry. The 1 car attached garage has an opener, and entrance from the house or backyard. There is a loft for extra storage. The fenced backyard has a patio and garden shed. There is extra parking on the front driveway The large tree in the backyard provides shade for those hot summer days.
